---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Chi Siamo | KriptyLab" description="Siamo architetti del software. Zero intermediari, zero fuffa, solo server e codice.">
  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-up">
        <span class="badge">Il Team</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="page-title reveal-up delay-100">Zero agenzie.<br/><span class="text-gradient">Solo Ingegneria.</span></h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle reveal-up delay-200">
        KriptyLab nasce per colmare un vuoto: le PMI italiane hanno bisogno di architetture solide, scalabili e sicure, non di "siti vetrina" venduti a peso d'oro da agenzie generaliste.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-cards">
      <div class="card about-card reveal-up delay-300">
        <div class="about-card-inner">
          <div class="about-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>L'Approccio "Bare Metal"</h2>
          <p>Eliminiamo i livelli di astrazione inutili. Scriviamo codice pulito, ottimizzato per le prestazioni, e configuriamo i server direttamente. Questo significa siti che caricano in frazioni di secondo e gestionali che non crollano sotto carico.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card about-card reveal-up delay-400">
        <div class="about-card-inner">
          <div class="about-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Privacy e AI On-Premise</h2>
          <p>Nell'era dell'Intelligenza Artificiale, i dati sono il tuo vero asset. Implementiamo LLM (Modelli Linguistici) direttamente sui server locali o su cloud privati europei. Nessun dato sensibile viene inviato a terze parti.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-page {
    padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-page::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 640px;
    text-wrap: balance;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .about-card-inner {
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-accent-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-border);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
